{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01BKPjomiWR9wia1mTFHqpJE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a thorough understanding of both failures, the history, and the codebase. Let me outline my proposed changes before writing the plan.\n\n**Key insights from my own analysis (correcting the feedback):**\n\n**Failure 1 (CHLEBEK):** The feedback claims the 25-candidate pre-filter cuts the real title because it has 6 words. But \"CHLEBEK Z WARZYWAMI I BOCZKIEM\" actually has **5 words** (`wordCount` = 5, which is ≤ 5), so the pre-filter's \"short first\" sort doesn't penalize it. The real root cause is different: if `bestStructural` resolves to \"WARZYWA I BOCZEK\" (which also qualifies as a structural heading) instead of the real title, the prefix filter at line 440 targets the wrong heading and \"CHLEBEK\" (a section header at position 8, followed by ingredients) survives to kill the real title via the \"shorter wins\" dedup rule.\n\n**Failure 2 (Faszerowana papryka):** The feedback is accurate — \"NA 3 PAPRYKI\" isn't caught as metadata and wins with allCapsBonus.\n\n**Proposed fixes:**\n1. Add Polish metadata patterns (including OCR-tolerant time-unit detection) to `looksLikeMetadata` — directly fixes Failure 2 and reduces noise in Failure 1\n2. Add pre-dedup sub-section header removal: if a short ALL_CAPS candidate is followed by ingredient lines AND is a substring of another surviving candidate, remove it before dedup — directly fixes Failure 1\n3. Add position/length tiebreaker to structural heading selection for robustness\n\nLet me write the improvement plan."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1403,"cache_read_input_tokens":49633,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1403},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f1cce918-fde6-46b5-9093-50476190ee9c","uuid":"9d293037-db64-4b45-a7c8-db81d9bf08cd"}
